{
  "stem": "25598.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Other people were too weak and too sick, so they stayed put in these huts, hoping that they'll gain some strength now that there was more food available.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I believe we stayed for a week or two, and then we-- we started on our way too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then on the way, Uncle Armin had some-- and-- and the babushka gave us some bottles of homemade vodka, which they gave us not for drinking, but they give it to us for bribing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if a truck of Russian soldiers would drive by and you'd give them a bottle of vodka, they'd let you ride with them for a few hours, or a few minutes, or what have you.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's what that was used for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So part of the way we had some rides with Russian soldiers, or with peasants with a carriage, with a horse.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Part of the way we walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But wherever we were, it was immediately behind the front lines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In some cities when we walked in, there was still street fighting, and there was bombing, and the water was poisoned.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at the same-- other times, we were walking on these fields and we had no food, and Russian planes would throw down canned food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it-- it would be a massive amount of the same kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like it would be-- for awhile it was these thick, very thick bars of chocolate, like army chocolate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would have that, and only that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For a while it was cans of caviar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to this day, I cannot stand the smell of caviar, because caviar is delicious if you eat it with something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But try and eat just caviar, it's not so delicious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But hey, if there's nothing else, you eat it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
